The paper discusses the use of data-driven, learnable methods for improving ultrasound image quality, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of machine learning algorithms for this purpose also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves the use of ultrasound imaging, which is a topic that falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
